title: Allenoconcha retinaculum
text:
Allenoconcha retinaculum is a <a href="species">species</a> of air-breathing <a href="land%20snail">land snail</a>, a <a href="Terrestrial%20animal">terrestrial</a> <a href="pulmonate">pulmonate</a> <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusc">mollusc</a> in the family <a href="Euconulidae">Euconulidae</a>. 
This species is <a href="endemic">endemic</a> to <a href="Norfolk%20Island">Norfolk Island</a>.
